main_body:
The Annex to Regulation (EC) No 877/2004 is amended as follows:
(a) ‘Sofia (BG)’ is added to the list of representative markets for the following products: ‘tomatoes’, ‘aubergines’, ‘watermelons’, ‘melons’, ‘apricots’, ‘peaches’, ‘table grapes’, ‘cerises’, ‘cucumbers’, ‘plums’ and ‘sweet peppers’;
(b) ‘Bucharest (RO)’ is added to the list of representative markets for the following products: ‘tomatoes’, ‘aubergines’, ‘water melons’, ‘apricots’, ‘apples’, ‘cerises’, ‘cucumbers’, ‘garlic’, ‘carrots’, ‘plums’, ‘sweet peppers’, ‘onions’ and ‘beans’.
